501 and Mkn421) at X-rays,\nsuggest that the low energy emitting electrons have a single log-normal flux\ndistribution while the high energy ones have a double log-normal flux\ndistribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Oct 2019 10:30:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
